<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039646" n="1"/>
    <opener><salute><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>J. U. Lic.</abbr> amico suo
<lb/><abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
            <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-140736662">Franciscus Christ</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Desiderium, quo maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> flagro certi aliquid de statu et valetudine
<lb/>tua percipiendi me diutius expectare non permittit, quo minus ad te
<lb/>scribam; dulcis quo<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> me lactat spes, <rs type="letter">literas</rs> meas aliquid tuarum elici<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>turas esse, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ne me spes fallat tuum est prospicere. Putavi equidem
<lb/>te pro nostra amicitia post tuum ad <rs type="place">Bernates</rs> adventum ad me aliquid
<lb/>esse exaraturum, sed cum jam tam multum temporis (ut mihi quidem
<lb/>videtur) sit elapsum nec quicquam interea de te cognoverim, maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
<lb/>me sub pectore versant cur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>; ex una enim parte subit te fortasse literis
<lb/>scribendis vacare non posse, quod maximo mihi esset dolori, te eousque
<lb/>studiis et laboribus esse astrictum, ut ne cum amicis quidem per
<lb/>literas colloqui possis; ex altera ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> parte major animum angit
<lb/>sollicitudo, te amicitiam et memoriam mei (quod Deus omen avertat!)
<lb/>plane ex animo tuo ejecisse, sed tamen pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> solatur et erigit tua
<lb/>mihi haud incognita integritas, quam non permissuram esse confido, ut
<lb/>statim ac oculos quis tuos aufugerit idem et animo tuo careat, quic<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>quid sit, paucis verbis me ex omnibus difficultatibus extrahere potens.
<lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1132220874">Jer. Raillard</rs> stat in procinctu intra paucos dies <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2660646">Genevam</rs> profecturus,
<lb/>mihi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> heri dixit, se per <rs type="place">Bernam</rs> iter facturum et te fortasse in tran<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>situ visurum, hunc finito isto mense sequetur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-123503094">Nic. Schwartz</rs>, adeo
<lb/>ut ab omnibus fer<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> amicis derelinquar; hic <abbr>N. S.</abbr> ante aliquod tempus
<lb/>Dissertationem conscripsit <rs type="biblio">de Querimoniis Jud<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>orum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Pontificiis scanda<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>lizatorum</rs>, quam sub Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sidio <abbr>D. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12209025X">Werenfelsii</rs> public<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> et mascul<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> qui<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dem defendit, nunc autem intra paucos dies examini, quod Candidati <abbr>S. S.</abbr>
<lb/>Ministerii subire tenentur, cum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1185612467">Abr. Sch<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ffer</rs> et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1185612734">Luca Hofman</rs> subjicietur;
<lb/>hi duo posteriores etiam <rs type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs>, in qua conscribenda occupatur <abbr>D. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-12209025X">Werenfels</rs> simul defendendam suscipient. <choice><abbr>Dnus</abbr><expan>Dominus</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-122123158">Grundeler</rs> <rs type="biblio">Disputationem
<lb/>Suam</rs> nondum publici juris fecit, credo autem hoc brevi factum iri,<note type="comment">Georg Friedrich Grundler aus Durlach disputierte am 6. Juni 1710 in Basel: Dissertatio inauguralis iuridica de restitutione famae / quam ... pro summis in utroque iure honoribus atque privilegiis doctoralibus solenniter consequendis ... die VI. Iunii M DCC X., Basileae, F. Lüdi, 1710. (Personeneintrag erstellen). </note> cum jam
<lb/>ad finem sit perducta. A <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1072469103">Henr. Beckio</rs> ante <date>octiduum</date> <rs type="letter">literas</rs> accepi,
<lb/>quibus me rogavit, ut salutem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter <rs type="person">alios amicos</rs> etiam tibi impertiam,
<lb/>simul<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> notum fecit, se studia Juris, post tam longum interregn<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> iterum
<lb/>tractanda suscepisse. Novi quod ad te scribam nihil habeo.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute>
<lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-03-08">8. Martii</date>, A <unclear><gap/></unclear></dateline>
